/*
Punch
Attack Spell
[OLD]
  Skill lvl        1        2        3         4        5
  Damage         r(6)+2  r(8)+3  r(10)+4   r(12)+5  r(14)+7   
  Cost             5        7        9         11       14
May gain a bonus if gloves are worn.
[NEW]
